ed by some voices, the Unruh effect\nlives among us.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 12 Jan 2017 18:30:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 22 Apr 2017 19:32:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-04-26"}
