antly flatter than in the\nhydrodynamical case. Although a two-phase medium arises in all cases, in the\nMHD simulations the cold phase is limited to lower densities.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 13 Jan 2017 15:09:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-03-08"}
