orm such a calibration and present our\nfindings on three different commercial products.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 12 Jan 2017 20:31:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 11 Dec 2017 15:07:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-03-28"}
